spx.sc.net

Interface HeartbeatState


  • public interface HeartbeatState
    Defines some of the various states that can be reported in heartbeats, although some applications may report more.

    These constants are kept in sync with the SPX_SCNET_HB_STATE_... constants in "SPxScNet.h".

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int CONNECTED
      Client is connected to server.
      static int DISCONNECTED
      Client is disconnected from server.
      static int INITIALISED
      Server is initialised.
      static int NOT_SET
      No state set.
